Package org.neo4j.server.web

Class Jetty9WebServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.neo4j.server.web.Jetty9WebServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    WebContainerThreadInfo, WebServer
    public class Jetty9WebServer
extends Object
implements WebServer, WebContainerThreadInfo
    This class handles the configuration and runtime management of a Jetty web server. The server is restartable.
